{"type":"article","id":3108,"title":"法广：12区爆冲突少女眼球被打碎警员扮示威者捉人兼疑插赃嫁祸，结果招来五毛疯狂洗地","uid":3012,"topics":[2549,2143,17],"contents":"法广报道的此条推特：<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RFI_Cn/status/1160844762447900674\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RFI_Cn/status/1160844762447900674</a><br>\n<br>\n部分报道：<br>\n“警方在尖沙嘴，疑违规以布袋弹瞄准一名黑衣少女的头部发射，布袋弹击穿少女的眼罩后，碎片疑再插入其右眼。根据苹果日报摄影记者的视频，可见少女眼部中弹后，已脱下口罩，口中不断涌出鲜血，但仍强忍剧痛，情绪不太激动，其后送院救治。该报公开摄记原片，并以黑白画面呈现，惟片段仍可能引起不安，收看前请留意。https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190812/59922249<br>\n<br>\n”<br>\n<br>\n这是警方的官方回应：“對於女示威者疑被海綿彈射穿眼罩、擊中右眼並致使眼部和臉骨重傷，警方表示「不能確定傷勢如何發生」，但表示當時有發射布袋彈。”<br>\n结果到了央视就成了队友误伤？？？？ 法广援引苹果日报的报道，招来五毛疯狂洗地，欢迎围观<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/EHXCyee.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EHXCyee.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/EHXCyee.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/coq4FSo.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/coq4FSo.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/coq4FSo.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZFOSFGl.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZFOSFGl.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZFOSFGl.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/qX71F2U.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qX71F2U.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qX71F2U.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/XudyHQV.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XudyHQV.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/XudyHQV.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zeca2ka.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zeca2ka.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zeca2ka.p